OL,3,CRobert Bush: live updates as Legacy
OL,4,Cfuneral director appears in court
OL,6,FA funeral director charged over an
OL,7,Finvestigation into the discovery of
OL,8,Fhuman remains at his premises is
OL,9,Fappearing at Hull Crown Court today.
OL,11,FRobert Bush, 47, was arrested in March
OL,12,F2024 after concerns were raised about
OL,13,F"care for the deceased" at Legacy
OL,14,FIndependent Funeral Directors in Hull.
OL,16,FIn a previous hearing, Bush denied 30
OL,17,Fcounts of preventing a lawful and
OL,18,Fdecent burial, relating to 30
OL,19,Fdifferent people, and one count of
OL,20,Ftheft from several charities.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
