OL,3,CRobert Bush: live updates as Legacy
OL,4,Cfuneral director appears in court
OL,6,FHe admitted more than 30 fraud charges.
OL,8,FThe hearing at Hull Crown Court is due
OL,9,Fto begin at 11am - there is live
OL,10,Fcoverage from the courtroom below.
OL,12,F11.26am - date set for sentencing
OL,14,FRobert Bush's sentencing hearing will
OL,15,Fstart on Monday 27th July. He has been
OL,16,Fgiven bail until that date.
OL,18,F11.16am - Robert Bush pleads guilty to
OL,19,Fall charges
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
