OL,3,CRobert Bush: live updates as Legacy
OL,4,Cfuneral director appears in court
OL,6,FRobert Bush has pleaded guilty to 30
OL,7,Fcounts of preventing lawful and decent
OL,8,Fburial of a dead body and one count of
OL,9,Ftheft.
OL,11,F11.05am - Robert Bush brought into
OL,12,Fcourt
OL,14,FRobert Bush has arrived in court
OL,15,Fwearing a dark suit and purple tie and
OL,16,Fthe hearing is underway.
OL,18,F10.45am - media called into court
