OL,3,CRobert Bush: live updates as Legacy
OL,4,Cfuneral director appears in court
OL,6,FThe media has been called into court
OL,7,Ffor the hearing which is due to start
OL,8,Fat 11am. Robert Bush is not yet in the
OL,9,Fdock.
OL,11,F8.55am - Robert Bush arrives at court
OL,13,FRobert Bush arrived at Hull Crown
OL,14,FCourt wearing a black face mask and a
OL,15,Fblack cap. He is due to appear in
OL,16,Fcourt at 11am.
